text: Reeuwijk-Brug is a village in the municipality of Bodegraven-Reeuwijk in the province of South Holland, the Netherlands. Reeuwijk-Brug has 7,770 inhabitants (2010). File:Aanzicht - Reeuwijk-Brug - 20185106 - RCE.jpg Category:Bodegraven-Reeuwijk Category:Populated places in South Holland
